name: Blob Finance
description:
The BLOB FINANCE smart contract applies a 4% fee on all transactions (buys/sells). Out of 
this, 2% is automatically distributed to holders, without farming! This means the 
amount of tokens in your wallet will forever increase as people transact. In addition, the BLOB TOKEN smart contract also takes 2% of each transaction and 
automatically adds it to the liquidity pool. The liquidity pool will continuously increase,
which leads to a higher price floor.
